# C# code style

## Private method naming

- Prefix every `private` method (including `private static` / `private async`) with `_`.
- Example: `PrintJson(...)` -> `_PrintJson(...)`

## Control flow

- Prefer early `return` over nested `if` blocks.
- Prefer early `continue`/`break` in loops for skip/stop cases.
- Keep the happy path at base indentation.

